{"tid":1540840,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Velvet的造型師又傻又瘋","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T11:43:00.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"aa1dcd25fba5b1ed30ca58e205a3d85abf87239d","tid":1540840,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:40:24.000Z","msg":"你跟我說這個是正常的衣服? 穿這樣真的可以出門嗎?<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/mCmtJvG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FmCmtJvG.jpg&h=25dc38f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPann Nate<br />\npost response:[+1,060][-59]<br />\n<br />\n1. [+483, -20] 我個人是覺得這樣對待年輕女孩，利用他們賺錢的公司是混蛋<br />\n<br />\n2. [+434, -15] 造型師是故意的&hellip;<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果去男性社群網站，會發現他們有很多對RedVelvet做性騷擾的評語，常常貼出關於她們的動圖。Red Velvet和Oh My Girl都常常被提到。說真的，如果要一直經營偶像市場，怎麼可以這樣對待女團呢?<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n3. [+362, -9] 他們已經這樣三年了&hellip;甚至連給他們適當的安全褲都沒有。如果看一下別的女團，安全褲應該是做成像熱褲的樣子&hellip;.這些批評已經很久了，但是他們還是一直這樣做&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n4. [+210, -4] SM老是要把頭埋在地板裡&hellip; 以前大家想到他們是明亮的概念，但是現在不是了TT TT 回到Red Flavor時期吧TT 他們很有才華，卻只能在這裡唱Umpah Umpah;;;<br />\n<br />\n5. [+119, -8] 但是制服被性別物化的概念，對空服員制服的批評更多..<br />\n<br />\n6. [+108, -25] 對我來說，自從SM用了lolita的概念後，我就不買他們的帳了<br />\n<br />\nPannChoa: <a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/y4ob82qq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fy4ob82qq&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=0298cf78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/y4ob82qq</a>"},{"pid":"6eee315b1009e362e4f46a1fcd27e154ac4743d5","tid":1540840,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:40:53.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"532129bff7308c60d4a4dc54d0dca54a6174d068","tid":1540840,"uid":256952,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:41:13.000Z","msg":"Irene人老西也老 著咩都冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"